Awesome window manager configuration and widget files

rc.lua		Main file
menu.lua	Menus
helpers.lua	Helper functions
clock.lua	Clock widget with multiple modes, calender and weather popup
volume.lua	Text volume widget
battery.lua	Battery widget with warning popups
mpd.lua		Music Player Daemon client with basic controls and info popup

Screenshot	http://i.imgur.com/Ik4b9.png

http://awesome.naquadah.org/
